paragraphs.title: 03.MD_Factura
paragraphs.text:
%livy2.sql
create table ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_md_factura as 
select concat(cod_tipocomp,'_',num_ruc,'_',num_seriecpe,'_',num_cpe) as llave_cpe,a.*,
        case when cod_moneda = 'USD' then mto_impcpe*3.35 else mto_impcpe end as mto_impcpe_soles,
        case when cod_moneda = 'USD' then mto_igvcpe*3.35 else mto_igvcpe end as mto_igvcpe_soles,
        case when cod_moneda = 'USD' then mto_vtacpe*3.35 else mto_vtacpe end as mto_vtacpe_soles,
        date_format(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fec_emicpe, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date),'u') as dia_semana_cpe,
        date_format(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fec_emicpe, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date),'d') as dia_mes_cpe,
        case when date_format(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fec_emicpe, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date),'d')<=3 then 'Inicio_mes[1-3]'
             when date_format(cast(to_date(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(fec_emicpe, 'yyyy-MM-dd'))) as date),'d')>=25 then 'Fin_mes[25-31]' 
             else "Otros[4-24]"
        end as dia_mes_cat,
        b.*,c.*
from (select cod_cpe as cod_tipocomp,num_ruc,num_serie_cpe as num_seriecpe,num_cpe,num_docide_recep as num_docidenti, cod_moneda,mto_importe_total as mto_impcpe,mto_total_igv as mto_igvcpe,mto_total_venta as mto_vtacpe,fec_emision as fec_emicpe from factura_electronica.t4241cabcpe_2019_02_v1 where cod_cpe = "01") a
left join ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_emi_ficha_nacional b on trim(a.num_ruc) = b.emi_ruc
inner join ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_rec_ficha_nacional c on trim(a.num_docidenti) = c.rec_ruc
where (rec_act_principal != emi_act_principal) and (rec_act_principal != nvl(emi_act_secun1,'emi_null1')) and (rec_act_principal != nvl(emi_act_secun2,'emi_null2')) and (nvl(rec_act_secun1,'rec_null1') != emi_act_principal) and (nvl(rec_act_secun1,'rec_null1') != nvl(emi_act_secun1,'emi_null1')) and (nvl(rec_act_secun1,'rec_null1') != nvl(emi_act_secun2,'emi_null2')) and (nvl(rec_act_secun2,'rec_null2') != emi_act_principal) and (nvl(rec_act_secun2,'rec_null2') != nvl(emi_act_secun1,'emi_null1')) and (nvl(rec_act_secun2,'rec_null2') != nvl(emi_act_secun2,'emi_null2'))

from pyspark.sql.types import StringType, IntegerType, StructType, StructField
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf, col
import unicodedata

class Test():
    def __init__(self,df):
        self.df = df
    
    def clearAccents(self,columns):
        validCols = [c for (c,t) in filter(lambda t: t[1] == 'string', self.df.dtypes)]
        if (columns == "*"): columns = validCols[:]
            
        def remove_accents(inputStr):
            nfkdStr = unicodedata.normalize('NFKD', inputStr)
            withOutAccents = u"".join([c for c in nfkdStr if not unicodedata.combining(c)])
            return  withOutAccents
        
        function = udf(lambda x: remove_accents(x) if x != None else x, StringType())
        exprs = [function(col(c)).alias(c) if (c in columns) and (c in validCols) else c for c in self.df.columns]
        self.df = self.df.select(*exprs)

%livy2.sql
create table ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_llaves_r as 
select llave_cpe,count(*) as N, sum(control) as Suma, sum(control)/count(*) as PropCom, 1-(sum(control)/count(*)) as PropDif
from
    (select llave_cpe, rec_act_principal, rec_act_secun1, rec_act_secun2,count,word,stem,nvl(control1,0) as control1,nvl(control2,0) as control2,nvl(control3,0) as control3 ,
        case when nvl(control1,0) + nvl(control2,0) + nvl(control3,0) >0 then 1 else 0 end as control
    from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_p_ll_r_procesado a
    left join (select w.*, '1' as control1 from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.words_gnd2_20181002 w) b on a.stem = b.cwords and trim(a.rec_act_principal) = trim(b.apy)
    left join (select w.*, '1' as control2 from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.words_gnd2_20181002 w) c on a.stem = c.cwords and trim(a.rec_act_secun1) = trim(c.apy)
    left join (select w.*, '1' as control3 from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.words_gnd2_20181002 w) d on a.stem = d.cwords and trim(a.rec_act_secun2) = trim(d.apy))
group by llave_cpe

%livy2.sql
create table ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_regimen as
select distinct vfp_numruc,R_GENERAL,R_MYPE,R_ESPECIAL,R_RUS,R_TOTAL,
    case when R_GENERAL = 1 then 'REGIMEN GENERAL'
         when R_MYPE = 1 then 'REGIMEN MYPE TRIBUTARIO'
         when R_ESPECIAL = 1 then 'REGIMEN ESPECIAL'
         when R_RUS = 1 then 'REGIMEN RUS'
         else 'R_OTROS'
    end as REGIMEN
from 
    (select a.vfp_numruc,R_GENERAL,R_MYPE,R_ESPECIAL,R_RUS,nvl(R_GENERAL,0)+nvl(R_MYPE,0)+nvl(R_ESPECIAL,0)+nvl(R_RUS,0) as R_TOTAL
    from (select distinct vfp_numruc from db_tributario.vfp_20190213) a 
    left join (select vfp_numruc, 1 as R_GENERAL from db_tributario.vfp_20190213 where vfp_codtri in ('030301','033101','035101','034101') group by 1) b on a.vfp_numruc = b.vfp_numruc
    left join (select vfp_numruc, 1 as R_MYPE from db_tributario.vfp_20190213 where vfp_codtri='031201') c on a.vfp_numruc = c.vfp_numruc
    left join (select vfp_numruc, 1 as R_ESPECIAL from db_tributario.vfp_20190213 where vfp_codtri='031101') d on a.vfp_numruc = d.vfp_numruc
    left join (select vfp_numruc, 1 as R_RUS from db_tributario.vfp_20190213 where substr(vfp_codtri,1,2) in ('04')) g on a.vfp_numruc = g.vfp_numruc
    )
order by 6 desc

%livy2.sql
create table ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_salida as
select a.*,nitems,descripcion,descripcion_limpio,n,suma,propcom,propdif,regimen
from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_md_factura a
left join (select llave_cpe,count(*) as nitems,concat_ws(' ** ',collect_list(trim(des_detitm))) as descripcion  from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_md_detalle group by llave_cpe) b on a.llave_cpe = b.llave_cpe
left join (select llave_cpe,concat_ws(' ** ',collect_list(trim(descripcion))) as descripcion_limpio from ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_palabras_llave_r_tabla group by llave_cpe) e on a.llave_cpe = e.llave_cpe
left join ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_llaves_r c on a.llave_cpe = c.llave_cpe
left join ds02_gastos_no_deducibles.201902_regimen d on trim(a.rec_ruc) = trim(d.vfp_numruc)
where regimen not in ('REGIMEN RUS','REGIMEN ESPECIAL') and rec_dependencia not in ('0011')
order by r_total desc
